{"tid":851112,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人知ig上面賣果d精靈係乜撚野黎","createTime":"2018-10-07T01:49:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T12:02:03.000Z","uid":130809,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"c1e37a3276109a481ad3b90b1e055cd94b2a126e","tid":851112,"uid":130809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T01:49:09.000Z","msg":"我見佢地賣到好撚貴 $900-$8000都有 <br />\n屌你老母擺張吸血新世紀個男主角張相就係高階7級吸血鬼 賣成$5200蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好以為呢d on99 實冇人買 我話你知係真係有人買 仲要好撚多 上ig hashtag#精靈 就會見到幾撚多精靈post同分享感受post <br />\n<br />\n支蠟燭個火郁一郁就話係精靈食緊又盛 我屌你啦 小小風吹支蠟燭個火都郁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  連唔洗等車唔洗等𨋢都係精靈幫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁同耶撚感恩有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n我一睇到就心諗今次發達啦賺到笑啦哈哈哈 所以我之前就開左間shop賣下精靈呀 魔法蠟燭呀 扮到似模似樣 結果真係有人問 心諗今次發過豬頭啦 但屌一單生意都未做得成就比d精靈擁有者撚狗咁撚鳩我 揭發我 話係黑店 屌 但其他店又唔見有人屌 又真係賣得出 其實係咪真係有精靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/07/093456_b03e80d07d6f1c4e8da142f50538d46a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F07%2F093456_b03e80d07d6f1c4e8da142f50538d46a.png&h=caab2e7f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/07/093459_cd0eeba5972349910bd6e1c62ad207fc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F07%2F093459_cd0eeba5972349910bd6e1c62ad207fc.png&h=617fda71&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/07/093500_7d9a246b32b5e3f00308db78cae2a8b5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F07%2F093500_7d9a246b32b5e3f00308db78cae2a8b5.png&h=57cb2ca0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/201